# Keg-only Homebrew formulae
# ==========================

# Some Homebrew formulae are "keg-only" and are not symlinked into the Homebrew
# prefix, so their binaries are not on the path by default. Uncomment the
# relevant line below to add one to the path when it is needed.

# libpq provides the PostgreSQL client tools, e.g. `psql` and `pg_dump`.
# pathadd "$(brew --prefix libpq)/bin"
